-- PetroChina Closes 130 Oil Wells at Liaohe Field for a Day Due to Flooding
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-07-23T00:26:18Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-23/petrochina-closes-oil-wells-at-liaohe-field-in-northeast-china-on-flooding.html

          
          
             PetroChina Co. shut 130 oil wells at
its Liaohe field in northeastern China because of flooding,
parent China National Petroleum Corp. said in its online
newsletter.  
 The one-day shutdown caused a 472 metric ton loss in
production, CNPC said.  
          
          


  


        